column1: Daily Weather Observations for Goulburn, New South Wales for December 2020
Prepared at 13:00 UTC on Sunday 10 October 2021   IDCJDW2049.202012
Most observations from Goulburn Airport, but some from Goulburn TAFE.

Cloud and evaporation observations are from Goulburn Tafe {station 070263}
